               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Ṣalota ʿǝṭan “Prayer of Incense” (fols. 3ra-66vb). 
 - Prayer of
                     Incense for Sunday (ba-ʾǝḥud) (fols. 46rb-66vb).
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>
